headline: GE HealthCare management to present at upcoming investor conference
summary: CHICAGO, December 29, 2025--GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC) is announcing that members of its management team will present at the JP Morgan 44th Annual Healthcare Conference in San Francisco, CA on January 13, 2026, at 10:30 a.m. PT/1:30 p.m. ET/12:30 p.m. CT.
